{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/pullrequests/12/comments/69168148.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/vrx/diff/osrf/vrx:1a0a5d353aa6..17c4805cb67d?path=wamv_gazebo%2Furdf%2Fwamv_gazebo_sensors.urdf.xacro"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx/pull-requests/12/_/diff#comment-69168148"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 12, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/pullrequests/12.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx/pull-requests/12"}}, "title": "Add sensor macros and example"}, "content": {"raw": "Would be possible to have a flag to enable/disable each sensor individually? Something like this:\n\n      <arg name=\"laser_enabled\" default=\"false\"/>\n      <arg name=\"kinect_enabled\" default=\"false\"/>\n    \n      <include file=\"$(find husky_gazebo)/launch/spawn_husky.launch\">\n        <arg name=\"laser_enabled\" value=\"$(arg laser_enabled)\"/>\n        <arg name=\"kinect_enabled\" value=\"$(arg kinect_enabled)\"/>\n      </include>\n\nMaybe this way, we only need a single URDF file.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Would be possible to have a flag to enable/disable each sensor individually? Something like this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;arg</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;laser_enabled&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">default=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;false&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;arg</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;kinect_enabled&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">default=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;false&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;include</span> <span class=\"na\">file=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;$(find husky_gazebo)/launch/spawn_husky.launch&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;arg</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;laser_enabled&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">value=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;$(arg laser_enabled)&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;arg</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;kinect_enabled&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">value=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;$(arg kinect_enabled)&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/include&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>Maybe this way, we only need a single URDF file.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-07-06T01:17:03.742436+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Carlos Ag\u00fcero", "uuid": "{da8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bda8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bda8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/692bf15758111acaddae4da15a47f9e5d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsCA-0.png"}}, "nickname": "caguero", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:4ded1ddf-947e-4154-bbd1-3dba24f1bdbd"}, "inline": {"to": 6, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "wamv_gazebo/urdf/wamv_gazebo_sensors.urdf.xacro"}, "updated_on": "2018-07-06T01:19:23.326631+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 69168148}